{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":402,"text":"I grew up in Bihar, India's poorest state,"},{"time":5411,"text":"and I remember when I was six years old,"},{"time":8877,"text":"I remember coming home one day to find a cart"},{"time":12643,"text":"full of the most delicious sweets at our doorstep."},{"time":17964,"text":"My brothers and I dug in,"},{"time":21453,"text":"and that's when my father came home."},{"time":24741,"text":"He was livid, and I still remember how we cried"},{"time":30205,"text":"when that cart with our half-eaten sweets"},{"time":34269,"text":"was pulled away from us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":37486,"text":"Later, I understood why my father got so upset."},{"time":42287,"text":"Those sweets were a bribe"},{"time":45512,"text":"from a contractor who was trying to get my father"},{"time":49093,"text":"to award him a government contract."},{"time":52556,"text":"My father was responsible for building roads in Bihar,"},{"time":57217,"text":"and he had developed a firm stance against corruption,"},{"time":61820,"text":"even though he was harassed and threatened."},{"time":65868,"text":"His was a lonely struggle, because Bihar"},{"time":69236,"text":"was also India's most corrupt state,"},{"time":72973,"text":"where public officials were enriching themselves,"},{"time":76735,"text":"[rather] than serving the poor who had no means"},{"time":80828,"text":"to express their anguish if their children"},{"time":84774,"text":"had no food or no schooling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":88607,"text":"And I experienced this most viscerally"},{"time":92964,"text":"when I traveled to remote villages to study poverty."},{"time":99262,"text":"And as I went village to village,"},{"time":103079,"text":"I remember one day, when I was famished and exhausted,"},{"time":109591,"text":"and I was almost collapsing"},{"time":111910,"text":"in a scorching heat under a tree,"},{"time":114940,"text":"and just at that time, one of the poorest men in that village"},{"time":120999,"text":"invited me into his hut and graciously fed me."},{"time":126915,"text":"Only I later realized that what he fed me"},{"time":131563,"text":"was food for his entire family for two days."},{"time":137306,"text":"This profound gift of generosity"},{"time":141729,"text":"challenged and changed the very purpose of my life."},{"time":147007,"text":"I resolved to give back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":150779,"text":"Later, I joined the World Bank, which sought to fight"},{"time":155083,"text":"such poverty by transferring aid from rich to poor countries."},{"time":160851,"text":"My initial work focused on Uganda, where I focused"},{"time":165883,"text":"on negotiating reforms with the Finance Ministry of Uganda"},{"time":170111,"text":"so they could access our loans."},{"time":172940,"text":"But after we disbursed the loans, I remember"},{"time":176071,"text":"a trip in Uganda where I found newly built schools"},{"time":180789,"text":"without textbooks or teachers,"},{"time":183573,"text":"new health clinics without drugs,"},{"time":186493,"text":"and the poor once again without any voice or recourse."},{"time":192276,"text":"It was Bihar all over again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":195852,"text":"Bihar represents the challenge of development:"},{"time":199812,"text":"abject poverty surrounded by corruption."},{"time":203723,"text":"Globally, 1.3 billion people live on less than"},{"time":207983,"text":"$1.25 a day, and the work I did in Uganda"},{"time":212692,"text":"represents the traditional approach to these problems"},{"time":217623,"text":"that has been practiced since 1944,"},{"time":221915,"text":"when winners of World War II, 500 founding fathers,"},{"time":227535,"text":"and one lonely founding mother,"},{"time":230971,"text":"gathered in New Hampshire, USA,"},{"time":233398,"text":"to establish the Bretton Woods institutions,"},{"time":236017,"text":"including the World Bank."},{"time":237822,"text":"And that traditional approach to development"},{"time":241122,"text":"had three key elements. First, transfer of resources"},{"time":245058,"text":"from rich countries in the North"},{"time":247009,"text":"to poorer countries in the South,"},{"time":249506,"text":"accompanied by reform prescriptions."},{"time":252399,"text":"Second, the development institutions that channeled"},{"time":255965,"text":"these transfers were opaque, with little transparency"},{"time":260727,"text":"of what they financed or what results they achieved."},{"time":264527,"text":"And third, the engagement in developing countries"},{"time":268440,"text":"was with a narrow set of government elites"},{"time":271722,"text":"with little interaction with the citizens, who are"},{"time":275036,"text":"the ultimate beneficiaries of development assistance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":279321,"text":"Today, each of these elements is opening up"},{"time":283522,"text":"due to dramatic changes in the global environment."},{"time":286882,"text":"Open knowledge, open aid, open governance,"},{"time":290577,"text":"and together, they represent three key shifts"},{"time":294322,"text":"that are transforming development"},{"time":297092,"text":"and that also hold greater hope for the problems"},{"time":300805,"text":"I witnessed in Uganda and in Bihar."}]},{"cues":[{"time":305378,"text":"The first key shift is open knowledge."},{"time":308344,"text":"You know, developing countries today will not simply"},{"time":311905,"text":"accept solutions that are handed down to them"},{"time":315502,"text":"by the U.S., Europe or the World Bank."},{"time":319129,"text":"They get their inspiration, their hope,"},{"time":321964,"text":"their practical know-how,"},{"time":324364,"text":"from successful emerging economies in the South."},{"time":327915,"text":"They want to know how China lifted 500 million people"},{"time":332595,"text":"out of poverty in 30 years,"},{"time":336258,"text":"how Mexico's Oportunidades program"},{"time":339204,"text":"improved schooling and nutrition for millions of children."},{"time":343900,"text":"This is the new ecosystem of open-knowledge flows,"},{"time":349562,"text":"not just traveling North to South, but South to South,"},{"time":354495,"text":"and even South to North,"},{"time":356798,"text":"with Mexico's Oportunidades today inspiring New York City."}]},{"cues":[{"time":362540,"text":"And just as these North-to-South transfers are opening up,"},{"time":366388,"text":"so too are the development institutions"},{"time":369228,"text":"that channeled these transfers."},{"time":371755,"text":"This is the second shift: open aid."},{"time":375624,"text":"Recently, the World Bank opened its vault of data"},{"time":379174,"text":"for public use, releasing 8,000 economic and social indicators"},{"time":384037,"text":"for 200 countries over 50 years,"},{"time":388406,"text":"and it launched a global competition to crowdsource"},{"time":392384,"text":"innovative apps using this data."},{"time":396051,"text":"Development institutions today are also opening"},{"time":399224,"text":"for public scrutiny the projects they finance."},{"time":403038,"text":"Take GeoMapping. In this map from Kenya,"},{"time":407303,"text":"the red dots show where all the schools financed by donors"},{"time":412022,"text":"are located, and the darker the shade of green,"},{"time":416014,"text":"the more the number of out-of-school children."},{"time":419374,"text":"So this simple mashup reveals that donors"},{"time":423510,"text":"have not financed any schools in the areas"},{"time":426486,"text":"with the most out-of-school children,"},{"time":428594,"text":"provoking new questions. Is development assistance"},{"time":432686,"text":"targeting those who most need our help?"},{"time":437305,"text":"In this manner, the World Bank has now GeoMapped"},{"time":440207,"text":"30,000 project activities in 143 countries,"},{"time":445149,"text":"and donors are using a common platform"},{"time":448325,"text":"to map all their projects."},{"time":451270,"text":"This is a tremendous leap forward in transparency"},{"time":456132,"text":"and accountability of aid."}]},{"cues":[{"time":458974,"text":"And this leads me to the third, and in my view,"},{"time":461970,"text":"the most significant shift in development:"},{"time":465302,"text":"open governance. Governments today are opening up"},{"time":469517,"text":"just as citizens are demanding voice and accountability."},{"time":473494,"text":"From the Arab Spring to the Anna Hazare movement in India,"},{"time":477524,"text":"using mobile phones and social media"},{"time":480258,"text":"not just for political accountability"},{"time":482872,"text":"but also for development accountability."},{"time":487017,"text":"Are governments delivering services to the citizens?"},{"time":491489,"text":"So for instance, several governments in Africa"},{"time":495634,"text":"and Eastern Europe are opening their budgets to the public."}]},{"cues":[{"time":500658,"text":"But, you know, there is a big difference between a budget"},{"time":504061,"text":"that's public and a budget that's accessible."},{"time":508098,"text":"This is a public budget. (Laughter)"},{"time":513018,"text":"And as you can see, it's not really accessible"},{"time":516123,"text":"or understandable to an ordinary citizen"},{"time":518842,"text":"that is trying to understand how the government is spending its resources."},{"time":523840,"text":"To tackle this problem, governments are using new tools"},{"time":527775,"text":"to visualize the budget so it's more understandable"},{"time":532458,"text":"to the public."},{"time":534658,"text":"In this map from Moldova, the green color shows"},{"time":538592,"text":"those districts that have low spending on schools"},{"time":542680,"text":"but good educational outcomes,"},{"time":545000,"text":"and the red color shows the opposite."},{"time":548249,"text":"Tools like this help turn a shelf full of inscrutable documents"},{"time":554776,"text":"into a publicly understandable visual,"},{"time":558530,"text":"and what's exciting is that with this openness,"},{"time":562296,"text":"there are today new opportunities for citizens"},{"time":566154,"text":"to give feedback and engage with government."},{"time":569680,"text":"So in the Philippines today, parents and students"},{"time":574063,"text":"can give real-time feedback on a website,"},{"time":578210,"text":"Checkmyschool.org, or using SMS, whether teachers"},{"time":583302,"text":"and textbooks are showing up in school,"},{"time":586096,"text":"the same problems I witnessed in Uganda and in Bihar."},{"time":590747,"text":"And the government is responsive. So for instance,"},{"time":593599,"text":"when it was reported on this website that 800 students"},{"time":598109,"text":"were at risk because school repairs had stalled"},{"time":602295,"text":"due to corruption, the Department of Education"},{"time":604886,"text":"in the Philippines took swift action."}]},{"cues":[{"time":607840,"text":"And you know what's exciting is that this innovation"},{"time":611537,"text":"is now spreading South to South, from the Philippines"},{"time":616199,"text":"to Indonesia, Kenya, Moldova and beyond."},{"time":620544,"text":"In Dar es Salaam, Tanzania, even an impoverished"},{"time":624803,"text":"community was able to use these tools"},{"time":628357,"text":"to voice its aspirations."},{"time":631329,"text":"This is what the map of Tandale looked like"},{"time":634248,"text":"in August, 2011. But within a few weeks,"},{"time":638601,"text":"university students were able to use mobile phones"},{"time":643067,"text":"and an open-source platform to dramatically map"},{"time":647617,"text":"the entire community infrastructure."},{"time":651104,"text":"And what is very exciting is that citizens were then"},{"time":655569,"text":"able to give feedback as to which health or water points"},{"time":660576,"text":"were not working, aggregated"},{"time":663450,"text":"in the red bubbles that you see,"},{"time":666050,"text":"which together provides a graphic visual"},{"time":670648,"text":"of the collective voices of the poor."},{"time":675103,"text":"Today, even Bihar is turning around and opening up"},{"time":680713,"text":"under a committed leadership that is making government"},{"time":683585,"text":"transparent, accessible and responsive to the poor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":688753,"text":"But, you know, in many parts of the world,"},{"time":692281,"text":"governments are not interested in opening up"},{"time":695259,"text":"or in serving the poor, and it is a real challenge"},{"time":700376,"text":"for those who want to change the system."},{"time":704720,"text":"These are the lonely warriors"},{"time":708289,"text":"like my father and many, many others,"},{"time":711753,"text":"and a key frontier of development work"},{"time":714877,"text":"is to help these lonely warriors join hands"},{"time":720073,"text":"so they can together overcome the odds."},{"time":723614,"text":"So for instance, today, in Ghana, courageous reformers"},{"time":728357,"text":"from civil society, Parliament and government,"},{"time":731557,"text":"have forged a coalition for transparent contracts"},{"time":735749,"text":"in the oil sector, and, galvanized by this,"},{"time":739805,"text":"reformers in Parliament are now investigating dubious contracts."},{"time":745485,"text":"These examples give new hope, new possibility"},{"time":750413,"text":"to the problems I witnessed in Uganda"},{"time":753525,"text":"or that my father confronted in Bihar."}]},{"cues":[{"time":758627,"text":"Two years ago, on April 8th, 2010, I called my father."},{"time":765596,"text":"It was very late at night, and at age 80,"},{"time":770994,"text":"he was typing a 70-page public interest litigation"},{"time":775795,"text":"against corruption in a road project."},{"time":779409,"text":"Though he was no lawyer, he argued the case in court"},{"time":784027,"text":"himself the next day. He won the ruling,"},{"time":788241,"text":"but later that very evening,"},{"time":790263,"text":"he fell, and he died."},{"time":794857,"text":"He fought till the end, increasingly passionate"},{"time":799801,"text":"that to combat corruption and poverty,"},{"time":803746,"text":"not only did government officials need to be honest,"},{"time":807753,"text":"but citizens needed to join together"},{"time":811002,"text":"to make their voices heard."},{"time":813897,"text":"These became the two bookends of his life,"},{"time":818758,"text":"and the journey he traveled in between"},{"time":821472,"text":"mirrored the changing development landscape."}]},{"cues":[{"time":826257,"text":"Today, I'm inspired by these changes, and I'm excited"},{"time":831210,"text":"that at the World Bank, we are embracing"},{"time":834314,"text":"these new directions, a significant departure"},{"time":837403,"text":"from my work in Uganda 20 years ago."},{"time":841281,"text":"We need to radically open up development"},{"time":844822,"text":"so knowledge flows in multiple directions,"},{"time":847626,"text":"inspiring practitioners, so aid becomes transparent,"},{"time":852417,"text":"accountable and effective, so governments open up"},{"time":856576,"text":"and citizens are engaged and empowered"},{"time":860522,"text":"with reformers in government."},{"time":862181,"text":"We need to accelerate these shifts."},{"time":865378,"text":"If we do, we will find that the collective voices"},{"time":870378,"text":"of the poor will be heard in Bihar,"},{"time":874768,"text":"in Uganda, and beyond."},{"time":876990,"text":"We will find that textbooks and teachers"},{"time":881065,"text":"will show up in schools for their children."},{"time":884102,"text":"We will find that these children, too,"},{"time":888185,"text":"have a real chance of breaking their way out of poverty."},{"time":894303,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"},{"time":897518,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}